OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy start with rain across
OL,6,FShetland soon clearing. It will then
OL,7,Fstay mostly dry with lengthening
OL,8,Fbright or sunny spells. A fresh
OL,9,Fsouthwesterly breeze.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA little brightness at first,
OL,12,Fotherwise a cloudy evening with some
OL,13,Flight and patchy rain. Becoming dry
OL,14,Fwith clear spells over Shetland
OL,15,Fovernight.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSunday:FDry and bright start for
OL,18,FShetland, otherwise a mostly cloudy
OL,19,Fday with patchy rain. Some haar at
OL,20,Ftimes over Shetland.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
