OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FSome
OL,6,Frain on Monday morning then becoming
OL,7,Fdry and bright. Breezy with sunshine
OL,8,Fand a few showers on Tuesday. Mostly
OL,9,Fsunny with light winds on Wednesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
